fields.description:
Declare a function in _alloy.js_
{code:javascript}
function test() {
    Ti.API.info("Hello!");
}
{code}

and try to invoke it in _index.js_ an you will see:

{code}
[ERROR] ReferenceError: Can't find variable: test
[ERROR] File: app.js
[ERROR] Line: 31
[ERROR] SourceId: <null>
[ERROR] Backtrace:
[ERROR]  undefined
{code}

on Android is working as well.
